{
  "sourceLanguage": "ja",
  "strings": {
    "": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": ""
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\n\n設定 > Pro にアップグレードから加入できます。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\n\nYou can subscribe from Settings > Upgrade to Pro."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    " のセッション": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": " session"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "—": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "—"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "（種目不明）": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "(Unknown exercise)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」とこのセッション内の %lld 件のセットを削除します。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Deletes \"%@\" and %lld sets in this session."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "「%1$@」とこのセッション内の %2$lld 件のセットを削除します。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」はライブラリにありません。カスタム種目として作成できます。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"%@\" is not in the library. You can create it as a custom exercise."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」を新規作成": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Create \"%@\""
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「1 回だけ挙げ切れる最大重量」のこと。直接測定は怪我のリスクが高いため、Oikomi は実際のセットから推定 1RM を計算します。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The maximum weight you can lift for a single rep. Because directly testing it carries a high injury risk, Oikomi calculates an Estimated 1RM from your actual sets."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「Hey Siri、ベンチプレスを記録」のように音声・ショートカット・スマートスタックから入力できる仕組みです。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A mechanism that lets you log via voice, Shortcuts, or Smart Stack, such as \"Hey Siri, log a bench press.\""
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「ヘルスケア」アプリで%@を記録すると、ここに推移が表示されます。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Record %@ in the Health app to see the trend here."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「最低限有効ボリューム」。これを下回ると筋量維持が難しくなる目安の週セット数で、部位別に設定されています。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Minimum Effective Volume (MEV). The approximate weekly set count below which maintaining muscle mass becomes difficult, set per muscle group."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「最大適応ボリューム」。これを超えると回復が追いつかず適応がむしろ減ってしまう目安の上限値です。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Maximum Adaptive Volume (MAV). The approximate upper limit above which recovery can't keep up and adaptation actually declines."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「分析」タブと AI コーチングカードで使われる指標です。コーチング判定はオンデバイスで計算され、外部に送信されません。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A metric used in the Analytics tab and AI coaching cards. Coaching assessments are computed on-device and are never sent externally."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「胸+三頭筋」「PPL: Push 日」など、複数種目をまとめたテンプレート。ホームから 1 タップで開始でき、種目順や前回重量がプリフィルされます。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A template that groups multiple exercises, such as \"Chest + Triceps\" or \"PPL: Push day.\" You can start it with one tap from Home, with exercise order and previous weights prefilled."
          }
        }
      }
    },
