    "★ お気に入り": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "★ Favorites"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "1 セットで扱う負荷。バーベル種目ではシャフトと付属プレートを合算した総重量を入力します。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The load handled in one set. For barbell exercises, enter the total weight combining the bar and the plates loaded on it."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "1 回のトレーニング全体を表す単位。開始時刻・終了時刻・含まれる全セットを保持し、終了時に HealthKit へ HKWorkout として書き込まれます。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A unit representing an entire workout. It holds the start time, end time, and all included sets, and is written to HealthKit as an HKWorkout when finished."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "1 回の挙上動作のこと。8 レップとは同じ重量で 8 回連続して挙げ切ったことを意味します。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A single lifting motion. 8 reps means lifting the same weight 8 times in a row to completion."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "1 種目に主働筋を 1 つ以上設定し、ボリューム集計時にはそれぞれフルカウントで加算します。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Each exercise can have one or more primary movers, each of which is fully counted when tallying volume."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "1 週間ほど強度を 80% 程度に意図的に落とす計画的な回復期間。連続トレーニング日数の長期化、または週ボリュームの急増を検知した時にコーチングカードで提案します。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A planned recovery period of about a week where intensity is intentionally dropped to around 80%. It is suggested via a coaching card when a long streak of consecutive training days or a sudden spike in weekly volume is detected."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "1〜10 レップ程度の中レップで精度が高い 1RM 推定式。業界で広く使われる標準式です。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A 1RM estimation formula that is accurate in the mid-rep range of about 1–10 reps. It is a standard formula widely used in the industry."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "1RM": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "1RM"
          }
        }
      }
    },
