    "Apple Watch で完結する筋トレ記録": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Strength training tracking, all on Apple Watch"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Apple Watch ワークアウトアプリ連携": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Apple Watch Workout app integration"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Apple Watch 標準ワークアウトと同じセッション (HKWorkoutSession) を共有します。Oikomi で記録を開始すると、Buddy 側にも自動でワークアウト中表示が出ます。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Shares the same session (HKWorkoutSession) as the standard Apple Watch workout. When you start logging in Oikomi, the Buddy side automatically shows a workout-in-progress display as well."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Apple のヘルスケアフレームワーク。Oikomi はワークアウト完了時に HKWorkout を書き込み (Free)、HRV / 安静時心拍 / 睡眠 / 体組成を読み取り (Pro) します。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Apple's health framework. Oikomi writes an HKWorkout when a workout finishes (Free), and reads HRV / resting heart rate / sleep / body composition (Pro)."
          }
        }
      }
    },
