            "value": "The difference between sets and %@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "セット数は「刺激の頻度」、%@ は「強度の総量」を表します。両方を合わせて見ると、追い込めているか・効率的かを判断できます。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Set count represents \"frequency of stimulus,\" while %@ represents \"total intensity.\" Looking at both together lets you judge whether you're pushing hard and training efficiently."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "セット編集": {
      "localizations": {
